      "description": "## [1.0.0] - 2026-07-15\r\n\r\n### Added\r\n- Initial release of Docket plugin\r\n- Responsive section grid with drag-and-drop functionality\r\n- Smart capture with inline tagging support\r\n- Semantic tagging system with custom colors\r\n- Task reminders with date/time pickers\r\n- Waiting time counters for tracking elapsed time\r\n- Archive system for completed tasks\r\n- Multi-tag filtering capabilities\r\n- Section customization (icons, colors, widths, descriptions)\r\n- Tag management with visual indicators\r\n- Desktop notifications for reminders\r\n- Light and dark mode support",
